# The upstream RAscore repo (code + models.zip, ~64 MB of trained models) is cloned on first use into
# vendor/RAscore at the pinned commit (see run.py::_ensure_vendor + README), and models.zip is unzipped
# there. Models/weights are NEVER committed (CLAUDE.md 0: never commit weights/data). The whole vendor
# tree is fetched on the box, so ignore it all.
vendor/RAscore/

# isolated pixi env (the box-solved lock is committed; the env itself is not)
.pixi/
